text: The food was amazing, especially their noodles. I also always frequent them for the breakfast set! Service was decent. highly recommend!
I ordered cheese mee hoon.  Very nice.  But will be even better if they hv chillies padi to go along it.
Love the cheese soup not too overwhelming. The prawns are fresh n big. Worth It
Food is nice and reasonably priced, they prepared my order relatively quick too.

This is a traditional local nasi lemak set. Blue pea dyed rice was fragrant and wing was crispy. Curry chicken was also yummy. Think thecurry will pair well with roti prata. Muslim friendly options. Great find here!
